dBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T05:15:09.000Z","msg":"佢話我煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我想買樣野俾佢 但驚佢唔鍾意 佢就話我煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同埋佢都好大男人 好雙重標準下<br />\n例如同一件事 佢就可以咁做但我就唔可以 真係勁乞人憎<br />\n佢平時同朋友去玩 我都唔會煩住佢迫佢覆我message<br />\n但我同朋友出街 我耐少少冇覆佢就嬲左我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我本身都少發脾氣 但唔代表我一啲脾氣都冇<br />\n佢發脾氣就大條道理 我嗰啲就無理取鬧 屌<br />\n就算我好理一咁同佢講 想佢聽返我有咩感受 佢都會躁返我轉頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee04a5096e47c934e53525437f6ce87c822fac01","tid":2118491,"uid":223320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4009f6c4deb3dba0f579171effb87ec1b5c8af61","tid":2118491,"uid":343873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5ea2f642284e1b474dec850a04a087ec5045a4ec","tid":2118491,"uid":223320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"eca0b6e6044978d58cd15f7203cced843e496530","tid":2118491,"uid":343873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T16:00:50.000Z","msg":"屌我明 呢啲真係好撚煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />郁啲就發脾氣<br />\n佢自己都有脾氣 但另一半就唔可以有少少脾氣<br />\n一發少少脾氣就會話你變左/以前唔係咁<br />\n同埋就算喊/都唔會氹返你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申：都同另一半鬧緊交<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T18:30:41.000Z","msg":"因咩事鬧交？<br />\n如果另一半有得嬲有得發脾氣 自己就唔可以有少少脾氣 都幾唔公平<br />\n好似俾人食住 對方冇咁愛自己咁<br />\n<br />\n我另一半本身就好少對我發脾氣 所以都唔想我發脾氣<br />\n有